  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/ea7f0e49e8355342cab33fe9398624d2.avif?t=1764869241\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><strong>Arrogue</strong> is a <strong>deck-building roguelike</strong> featuring <strong>turn-based</strong>, <strong>physics-driven combat</strong> against dangerous enemies.<br>To succeed, you'll need to collect and upgrade powerful <strong>arrows</strong> and <strong>relics</strong> while making strategic decisions during random events.<br>But beware, death is permanent. If you die, you'll have to start over from the beginning.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/2d1d2e884bf165510c2bc5093f3438d1.poster.avif?t=1764869241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/2d1d2e884bf165510c2bc5093f3438d1.webm?t=1764869241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/2d1d2e884bf165510c2bc5093f3438d1.mp4?t=1764869241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/3cb0ccb4343bd796fcc8e81f2c2cbf9b.avif?t=1764869241\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Shoot your way to victory</strong>: Shoot powerful arrows to destroy everything in your way, either to kill every enemy, collect buffs, heal yourself or to collect money.</li><li><strong>Make strategic choices</strong>: Find the right path, collect the arrows and relics that suit your needs, protect the village while trying to stay alive.</li><li><strong>Find the best synergies</strong>: With 140+ relics, 50+ arrows and 4 playable characters you have a ton of ways to win. Shoot 10 arrows at once, spread fire to the whole board, poison every enemy, kill every enemy with debris or shoot directly at them..</li><li><strong>Too easy for you?</strong>: Unlock difficulties for each character until it is challenging enough. Will you be able to win all difficulties on every character?</li><li><strong>Endless mode</strong>: Do you want to continue your build after winning? Play endless mode, find different ways of breaking the game and compete against other in an online leaderboard</li><li><strong>Appease your completionist instincts</strong>: Arrogue has endless replayability with challenging achievements.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/14343a727ba0b0cb6d0affeedd070b3e.poster.avif?t=1764869241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/14343a727ba0b0cb6d0affeedd070b3e.webm?t=1764869241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/14343a727ba0b0cb6d0affeedd070b3e.mp4?t=1764869241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/dae37024437e08d34d27eeb899588820.avif?t=1764869241\" width=600 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/3b152281819fa8b2fd8c011484367c05.poster.avif?t=1764869241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/3b152281819fa8b2fd8c011484367c05.webm?t=1764869241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/3b152281819fa8b2fd8c011484367c05.mp4?t=1764869241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>About the dev</strong>:<br>I'm <strong>PIPAPOU</strong>, the solo dev of Arrogue. I've done everything in this game except (most) graphics, music and sound design.<br>I'm trying to craft you the best experience possible but as a solo dev it takes some time, that's why the game is in early access.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/ea7f0e49e8355342cab33fe9398624d2.avif?t=1764869241\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><strong>Arrogue</strong> is a <strong>deck-building roguelike</strong> featuring <strong>turn-based</strong>, <strong>physics-driven combat</strong> against dangerous enemies.<br>To succeed, you'll need to collect and upgrade powerful <strong>arrows</strong> and <strong>relics</strong> while making strategic decisions during random events.<br>But beware, death is permanent. If you die, you'll have to start over from the beginning.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/2d1d2e884bf165510c2bc5093f3438d1.poster.avif?t=1764869241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/2d1d2e884bf165510c2bc5093f3438d1.webm?t=1764869241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/2d1d2e884bf165510c2bc5093f3438d1.mp4?t=1764869241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/3cb0ccb4343bd796fcc8e81f2c2cbf9b.avif?t=1764869241\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Shoot your way to victory</strong>: Shoot powerful arrows to destroy everything in your way, either to kill every enemy, collect buffs, heal yourself or to collect money.</li><li><strong>Make strategic choices</strong>: Find the right path, collect the arrows and relics that suit your needs, protect the village while trying to stay alive.</li><li><strong>Find the best synergies</strong>: With 140+ relics, 50+ arrows and 4 playable characters you have a ton of ways to win. Shoot 10 arrows at once, spread fire to the whole board, poison every enemy, kill every enemy with debris or shoot directly at them..</li><li><strong>Too easy for you?</strong>: Unlock difficulties for each character until it is challenging enough. Will you be able to win all difficulties on every character?</li><li><strong>Endless mode</strong>: Do you want to continue your build after winning? Play endless mode, find different ways of breaking the game and compete against other in an online leaderboard</li><li><strong>Appease your completionist instincts</strong>: Arrogue has endless replayability with challenging achievements.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/14343a727ba0b0cb6d0affeedd070b3e.poster.avif?t=1764869241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/14343a727ba0b0cb6d0affeedd070b3e.webm?t=1764869241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/14343a727ba0b0cb6d0affeedd070b3e.mp4?t=1764869241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/dae37024437e08d34d27eeb899588820.avif?t=1764869241\" width=600 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/3b152281819fa8b2fd8c011484367c05.poster.avif?t=1764869241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785570/extras/3b152281819fa8b2fd8c011484367c05.webm?t=1764869241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"http